  "text": "4. Our survey instruments (Appendix II) may have introduced a self-report bias [CITATION_1] . Subjects may respond to questions in ways they thought would please the researchers or in ways that corresponded to what they wished was true, their ideal self on an ideal day. As such, we acknowledge that because all responses to the survey questions were self reports, they may deviate somewhat from reality. The survey instruments were validated in other studies and they were minimally adapted for the purposes of this study.",
